title: subsections (1) and (2) of section 9 of the Finance Act 2022 (No. 44 of 2022)
heading: 2. The 1st day of January 2024 is appointed as the day on which
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of January 2024 is appointed as the day on which 
subsections (1) and (2) of section 9 of the Finance Act 2022 (No. 44 of 2022) 
shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

13 December, 2023. 

MICHAEL MCGRATH, 
Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 15th December, 2023.
